<?xml version="1.0"?>
<!DOCTYPE softwarelist SYSTEM "softwarelist.dtd">
<!--
license:CC0-1.0

Colonial Data Services SB-80 (colonial/sb80.cpp) 8" floppies.

The bootable system disks here carry Dave Rand's v1.22 CBIOS
("SB 80 CP/M 2.2 61K Version 1.22  Dave Rand  04/15/84").  The Maslin
dumps are Teledisk (.td0); the curated/recovery images are ImageDisk
(.imd).  The driver registers both readers.

Provenance and third-party terms for the underlying disks are documented
in the preservation repository (github: davidlrand/mame-system-media,
colonial-sb80/README.md and LICENSE).
-->
<softwarelist name="sb80_flop" description="Colonial Data Services SB-80 floppies">

	<software name="cpm">
